readable.content: One bicyclist runs alongside her bike , while another rides up behind . One biker is running with their bike while another is riding around them . The bike rider runs with his red bike while another gains on him , both wearing green outfits and black helmets . Two biker in black-green , first is pushing her bike , the second is riding hers . Two people with bicycles , one in front running with a bike and one in back riding .
